    "num": "02",
    "deck": "<div class=\"wrap\"><div class=\"eyebrow anim\"><span class=\"num\">02</span><span class=\"bar\"></span>Orientation</div><h2 class=\"head anim\">Poll: Your Understanding of 'Texican'</h2><ul><li>Share your initial definition or associations with 'Texican'</li><li>Compare with peers' responses</li><li>Prepare to contrast with historical definitions</li></ul><p class=\"lede anim\">This interactive poll invites learners to express their current understanding of 'Texican.' Gathering diverse perspectives sets the stage for deeper exploration and correction of misconceptions. <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s2\">[2]</sup> <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s7\">[7]</sup></p><div class=\"lesson-detail anim\"><p><strong>Example:</strong> A learner might associate 'Texican' simply with Texans of Hispanic descent, while another might link it to a specific historical period or cultural group.</p><p><strong>Practice:</strong> Submit your definition or thoughts on 'Texican' now.</p><p><strong>Watch for:</strong> Assuming all learners share the same baseline knowledge about Texican identity.</p></div></div>",
